OL,3,CLondon Marathon could be a two-day
OL,4,Cevent in 2027 to allow more
OL,5,Cparticipants
OL,7,FLondon Marathon organisers are
OL,8,Fexploring the possibility of staging
OL,9,Fthe event across two days in 2027 to
OL,10,Fallow more people to take part.
OL,12,FA world record-setting 1,133,813
OL,13,Frunners applied through the public
OL,14,Fballot to participate in this year's
OL,15,Fevent ` taking place on April 26 `
OL,16,Fwhich represents a 36 per cent year-on-
OL,17,Fyear increase and nearly doubling the
OL,18,Fapplication pool from 2024.
