OL,3,CLondon Marathon could be a two-day
OL,4,Cevent in 2027 to allow more
OL,5,Cparticipants
OL,7,FLast year's London Marathon raised the
OL,8,Fmost money in the event's history,
OL,9,F#87.3million, and set a Guinness World
OL,10,FRecord for the number of finishers in
OL,11,Fa single marathon after 56,640 crossed
OL,12,Fthe line despite sweltering conditions
OL,13,Fin the capital.
OL,15,FA London Marathon spokesperson said:
OL,16,F"The TCS London Marathon is the
OL,17,Fworld's most popular marathon, and we
OL,18,Fare continually exploring innovative
OL,19,Fways to enable more people to take
OL,20,Fpart, while delivering positive
OL,21,Fbenefits for London.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
