OL,3,CLondon Marathon could be a two-day
OL,4,Cevent in 2027 to allow more
OL,5,Cparticipants
OL,7,F"Together with our partners and
OL,8,Fstakeholders, we are looking at the
OL,9,Fintention for the 2027 TCS London
OL,10,FMarathon to take place across two days.
OL,12,F"No approval has been given at this
OL,13,Fstage. Our immediate focus is on
OL,14,Fdelivering an incredible 2026 TCS
OL,15,FLondon Marathon on Sunday 26 April and
OL,16,Fensuring every participant has an
OL,17,Famazing experience."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@TO]
