OL,3,CLondon Marathon could be a two-day
OL,4,Cevent in 2027 to allow more
OL,5,Cparticipants
OL,7,FAccording to a report in the Guardian,
OL,8,Fthe one-off event would expand the
OL,9,FLondon Marathon to 100,000
OL,10,Fparticipants and potentially split the
OL,11,Fmen's and women's elite races across
OL,12,Fthe weekend.
OL,14,FA Mayor of London spokesperson said:
OL,15,F"London is the sporting capital of the
OL,16,Fworld and the Mayor looks forward to
OL,17,Fworking with London Marathon partners
OL,18,Fto consider if it might be possible to
OL,19,Fhost an event that will run across two
OL,20,Fdays next year."
OL,26,@wD@AOU|D@PO]
